{"tid":1657562,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中北美洲國家聯賽","createTime":"2019-10-16T06:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T12:21:21.000Z","uid":34572,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"0498b377b4dce1dccb53c7ffb91154e765211150","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://league-mp7static.mlsdigital.net/styles/image_landscape/s3/images/concacaf-nations-league-2018.png?dCgbYYYjZne9aJuT38s4LEz9InZaH014&amp;itok=IVokKnW5&amp;c=08ce797bb0b111f4ccfb5e64e152df15\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fleague-mp7static.mlsdigital.net%2Fstyles%2Fimage_landscape%2Fs3%2Fimages%2Fconcacaf-nations-league-2018.png%3FdCgbYYYjZne9aJuT38s4LEz9InZaH014%26itok%3DIVokKnW5%26c%3D08ce797bb0b111f4ccfb5e64e152df15&h=57b4ec1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>中北美洲及加勒比海國家聯賽（CONCACAF Nations League）</strong><br />\n<br />\n41個中北美洲及加勒比海足協嘅成員都會參與<br />\n<br />\nCONCACAF Nations League制度嘅promotion同外圍賽抽籤儀式：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzYIkCWAiRE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDzYIkCWAiRE&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=2fa5bedd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DzYIkCWAiRE</a><br />\n<br />\n成個聯賽分League A, B, C。League A分4組，每組3隊。League B分4組，每組4隊。League C分4組，其中3組3隊，剩低一組有4隊。喺41隊全部都會參加嘅情況之下<br />\n<br />\nLeague B, C每組首名將會升班<br />\n<br />\nLeague A, B每組包尾將會降班<br />\n<br />\nLeague A每組小組首名又係會進入最後四強淘汰賽，爭奪最後冠軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2018年世界盃中北美洲外圍賽最後一圈嘅六隊，即係墨西哥、哥斯達黎加、巴拿馬、洪都拉斯、美國、千里達，直接入League A。<br />\n<br />\n其餘CONCACAF成員將會各踢四場外圍賽（主客各二）決定League A, B, C。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n由於危地馬拉俾FIFA ban咗，所以今次嘅外圍賽將會得34隊參加。34隊先分4個Tier，Tier A同Tier D有8隊，Tier B同Tier C就會有9隊：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/193843_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F193843_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=cb34855d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTier A<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194021_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194021_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=33c9a08d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTier B<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194116_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194116_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=b91424a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTier C<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194253_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194253_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=67fef870&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTier D<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194353_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194353_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=20ed0e8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外圍賽賽程<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194432_ca3c7cfa6f486eb8568e385a03b95c3a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194432_ca3c7cfa6f486eb8568e385a03b95c3a.png&h=5b4b0346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n想知點編嘅可以自己睇由37分開始睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n外圍賽最終排名將會決定League A, B, C<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/18/194629_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F18%2F194629_8d67561f76ba1e76c2471138fa2b14c4.png&h=57a80cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外圍賽最終排名：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uLEZVcK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuLEZVcK.png&h=f61a992b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9sZOOxM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9sZOOxM.png&h=2f33a2e0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正賽分組抽籤喺三月時抽咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JuGkm_Pe65g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJuGkm_Pe65g&d=TC1Ad7l9MtPLjBCdpR1LVirXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=9a560de0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JuGkm_Pe65g</a><br />\n<br />\n而聯賽喺上個月已經開咗League，但因為太多事發生搞到我唔記得咗開post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加拿大贏美國咁多人講先remind返我有中北美洲國家聯賽呢回事<br />\n<br />\nPS：我上年開post講外圍賽階段時唔知道危地馬拉會ban幾耐所以假設咗佢唔會踢今季國家聯賽，但佢喺抽籤前解咗ban，所以編咗入League C A組"},{"pid":"31e6fdc1e46dcde49531d73b21c85cc2a124cf40","tid":1657562,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:56:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dC4rszp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdC4rszp.jpg&h=a54a4986&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fb3808c03a182d2c1c14a9d9bb89ad5585e955a4","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:01:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">既然我遲咗開post，咁就順便回顧下頭幾輪嘅波先喇</span></span>"},{"pid":"f16dbba5c5c5200a7fedcd5e28e8b6ad372689ad","tid":1657562,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"香港入去踢可以排第幾？"},{"pid":"f6d081a5e6d7b35115dfee3d34af9b2605df5656","tid":1657562,"uid":30768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"唔好偷人文啦，成篇文啲字都啱點會係你寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ebcba0496f6f8d36fc3a0bcf1eb778b3024d1f","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f16dbba5c5c5200a7fedcd5e28e8b6ad372689ad","tid":1657562,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"香港入去踢可以排第幾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:05:13.000Z","msg":"麥狗一日仲領軍，香港隊連荷屬馬丁島都贏唔到"},{"pid":"facc46332ed078a56e2e7f3f6c55c2df60f63d1e","tid":1657562,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f16dbba5c5c5200a7fedcd5e28e8b6ad372689ad","tid":1657562,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:03:25.000Z","msg":"香港入去踢可以排第幾？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:05:19.000Z","msg":"外圍賽"},{"pid":"738ced7cef01fffd15276230bb87b95931514192","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6d081a5e6d7b35115dfee3d34af9b2605df5656","tid":1657562,"uid":30768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"唔好偷人文啦，成篇文啲字都啱點會係你寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"我偷我上年嘅post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82232480875ce55b233f87e37b8b1d91f7932ef0","tid":1657562,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"依啲聽都未聽過嘅島國足總有錢比佢哋飛黎飛去踢垃圾波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4d2f21e4e7869eaee628c469b34db9c76be4741","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"PS：我上年開post講外圍賽階段時唔知道危地馬拉會ban幾耐所以假設咗佢唔會踢今季國家聯賽，但佢喺抽籤前解咗ban，所以編咗入League C <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">C</span></span>組"},{"pid":"d930570572b800cbaf75227cef5a463699c97bb4","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:14:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">League C</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UprQ1Z7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUprQ1Z7.png&h=af7b00b7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n比歐國聯嘅League D更加獵奇feel，唔講呢啲島國大家未必知實際位置喺邊，基本上有啲連FIFA會員都唔係，又或者本身一年都唔知有冇一埸正亠比賽，國家聯賽令到呢啲島仔有固定比賽踢下，都幾唔錯架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6783854373606b6ed5310589593d52f869789559","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:14:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">League C</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UprQ1Z7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUprQ1Z7.png&h=af7b00b7&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n比歐國聯嘅League D更加獵奇feel，唔講呢啲島國大家未必知實際位置喺邊，基本上有啲連FIFA會員都唔係，又或者本身一年都唔知有冇一埸正式比賽，國家聯賽令到呢啲島仔有固定比賽踢下，都幾唔錯架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"9cbb9501e013187b33bf31e357430b50d3bb6275","tid":1657562,"uid":202348,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"2018年世界盃中北美洲外圍賽最後一圈嘅六隊，即係墨西哥、哥斯達黎加、巴拿馬、洪都拉斯、美國、千里達，直接入League A。<br />\n<br />\n六隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd065b2d105ed37c103922232b501c4c40bca811","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cbb9501e013187b33bf31e357430b50d3bb6275","tid":1657562,"uid":202348,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:16:24.000Z","msg":"2018年世界盃中北美洲外圍賽最後一圈嘅六隊，即係墨西哥、哥斯達黎加、巴拿馬、洪都拉斯、美國、千里達，直接入League A。<br />\n<br />\n六隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:16:45.000Z","msg":"屌你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b454d3833e51814a2302aae42278cd99c410c1","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"82232480875ce55b233f87e37b8b1d91f7932ef0","tid":1657562,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:07:25.000Z","msg":"依啲聽都未聽過嘅島國足總有錢比佢哋飛黎飛去踢垃圾波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"CONCACAF補水囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d3ca4bf54d2e1b16e0c6ba21c35a192ed3d803","tid":1657562,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e4d2f21e4e7869eaee628c469b34db9c76be4741","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"PS：我上年開post講外圍賽階段時唔知道危地馬拉會ban幾耐所以假設咗佢唔會踢今季國家聯賽，但佢喺抽籤前解咗ban，所以編咗入League C <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">C</span></span>組"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:18:53.000Z","msg":"cc組同cc台有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7a1ff06bfa46c14338a4e8745e8a82f81ad5304","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:28:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RrAyfqT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRrAyfqT.png&h=f00ab34d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n相對而言，League B我覺得係海軍鬥水兵，因為呢度好多隊都係抽到好籤唔駛打勁啲嘅隊先至叫做入到League B<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d1abcfcb6655c8b220c0d80e0942506e06420a","tid":1657562,"uid":1734,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:29:51.000Z","msg":"美國輸左 香港玩完？"},{"pid":"61696e639bad39984d5edbecdb00cf2fa7c72444","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3NAqQZo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3NAqQZo.png&h=94f4a297&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n同歐國聯一樣，最受注目嘅始終都係League A。值得留意嘅係，League A有兩隊唔係FIFA成員嚟，分別係馬提尼克同庫拉索，呢兩隊如果有留意今年嘅美洲金盃嘅話，呢兩隊都踢得唔差架，庫拉索甚至入埋淘汱賽階段添，而佢地喺國家聯賽嘅表現都冇大跌watt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5827259554acec41cec57a23ccfa812431096926","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:39:21.000Z","msg":"漏咗講，同歐國聯一樣，為咗令到各隊有參賽誘因，中北美洲國家聯賽都作為美洲金盃外圍賽嘅一部份<br />\nLeague C嘅小組首名同League B嘅小組次名將會晉身下屆美洲金盃嘅外圍賽Round 1<br />\nLeague B嘅小組首名同League A嘅小組首次名更加係會直入下屆美洲金盃決賽週<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f1e4d62284eab3c40ce9a89bd8bbb1a94de2e6","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:52:56.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">League C A組</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s7VN4pw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs7VN4pw.png&h=a4717534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9bESv4w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9bESv4w.png&h=248fef6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hZUja4x.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhZUja4x.png&h=809ceb9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RbOcv4y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRbOcv4y.png&h=30bdeae1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rNhQhKy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrNhQhKy.png&h=decf1dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLeague C惟一有四隊嘅小組，巴巴多斯同開曼群島實力稍微高一啲，而美屬處女島嘅實力明顯係差一截。開曼群島其實四場外圍賽都唔差，抽到壞籤一場都贏唔到都未致於話炒到一獲金，但偏偏正賽就作客俾外圍賽惟二0分嘅法屬聖馬丁島炒三粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47e579ee4db6430ba903c20a7efc13e0db29f171","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:02:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>League C B組</ins></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2MLKnff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2MLKnff.png&h=aee9cc01&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LQqN4tB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLQqN4tB.png&h=0b4dbe97&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aimp6GW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Faimp6GW.png&h=78b55b54&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n三隊喺外圍賽都係得一分，但明顯地英屬處女島係差一截，特別係防守力，主場3-4輸俾博奈爾呢場波，講緊係84分鐘領先到3-1，結果俾人地連入三球反cup<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff815cb11efb619220c190e7978554390874591","tid":1657562,"uid":59966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e4d2f21e4e7869eaee628c469b34db9c76be4741","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"PS：我上年開post講外圍賽階段時唔知道危地馬拉會ban幾耐所以假設咗佢唔會踢今季國家聯賽，但佢喺抽籤前解咗ban，所以編咗入League C <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">C</span></span>組"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"3場入20失0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a46256cdad70ad9784d9ff0c0debba0bee1e2296","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:11:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>League C C組</ins></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/znpWdpL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FznpWdpL.png&h=c73cfad8&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fL9CHh7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfL9CHh7.png&h=58ff1dfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GAVKnh6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGAVKnh6.png&h=2154851b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n冇乜好講，事實上本身作為中北美洲中遊份子嘅危地馬拉，唔係俾FIFA ban咗而冇得踢外圍賽嘅話，佢基本上係League B上遊。不過波多黎各其實都值得一提，佢外圍賽四場都只係輸一球起兩球止，如果唔係抽到同危地馬拉同組嘅，其實應該有得爭下升班資格"},{"pid":"acd6fb5732d9b10bfae2e803f25feda20cb2d462","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":1,"dislike":