\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG2qeKAJ.png&h=e2f07b44&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WXR5RfK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWXR5RfK.png&h=567e6aaa&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n另一組冇咩好講嘅組別，瓜德羅普本身嘅外圍賽抽中咗馬提尼克同庫拉索<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 超班之下結果屈你特克斯與凱科斯群島同荷屬聖馬丁島機都好正常。而瓜德羅普雖然唔係FIFA成員，但就係亨利、沙夏、加拿斯、杜林、韋托特等法國名宿嘅家鄉嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d68f4cd99c05c0cf3f2ce423c080ede6e1447bf1","tid":1657562,"uid":199081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"2018年世界盃中北美洲外圍賽最後一圈嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">六弟</span>，即係墨西哥、哥斯達黎加、巴拿馬、洪都拉斯、美國、千里達，直接入League A。<br />\n<br />\n改返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1960313ec7b4553e61165e22de367dead984d16a","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d68f4cd99c05c0cf3f2ce423c080ede6e1447bf1","tid":1657562,"uid":199081,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"2018年世界盃中北美洲外圍賽最後一圈嘅<span style=\"color: red;\">六弟</span>，即係墨西哥、哥斯達黎加、巴拿馬、洪都拉斯、美國、千里達，直接入League A。<br />\n<br />\n改返啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:42:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44aefc85ba6120808f4a4c72fb02cea07f7bf437","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T08:55:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">League B A組</span></ins></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AN3PyEk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAN3PyEk.png&h=bb2f5a7d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7yVFFjm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7yVFFjm.png&h=27e5c129&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0BUKL2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0BUKL2.png&h=149f0397&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ydt74L3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fydt74L3.png&h=d6b122d0&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ZVeKL4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ZVeKL4.png&h=993d531d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n4隊喺外圍賽都兩勝兩負，其實我對法圭會失望少少，畢竟法圭都算係加勒比海中上遊，即使近年差咗，都未至於會踢咗四場，連小組頭兩名嘅資格都確立唔到下話......格林納達就正常水準，如無意外小組首名升班同再入美洲金盃"},{"pid":"4e7c1ef17393c769595953210d64b830b55cd374","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:08:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>League B B組</ins></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7c5FFna.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7c5FFna.png&h=fc32fb6e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JRZjbtQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJRZjbtQ.png&h=579dda8b&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbBNknf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbBNknf.png&h=40f4d5de&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xwyG9fB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxwyG9fB.png&h=a025482c&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dnfm9fC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdnfm9fC.png&h=09e5ec1f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n牌面上兩隊中美洲份子實力較稍強，不過多明尼加上場贏唔到聖露西亞，又輸埋比蒙塞拉特島；本身應該係再高出一截嘅薩爾瓦多又偏偏第二場作客輸比多明尼加，充份反映到我所講League B係海軍鬥水兵嘅情況，暫時都冇一隊肯定到排名，不過聖露西亞如無意外都應該會降班"},{"pid":"85d8550ba16d67c77a219a1cab458576e06a64de","tid":1657562,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:24:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><ins>League B C組</ins></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EDvZbzd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEDvZbzd.png&h=25554c94&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V5wEV0U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV5wEV0U.png&h=9d8c7478&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/feUCHFV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfeUCHFV.png&h=173e847e&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L4bp67B.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL4bp67B.png&h=fae16733&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GxYgdNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGxYgdNC.png&h=5dd314a9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nLeague B入面惟一一隊冇咩懸念嘅小組。牙買加作為加勒比一哥，美洲金盃常客，基本上喺呢組都係超晒班，拎多分就可以升上League A同殺入下屆美洲金盃決賽週。而包尾嘅阿魯巴本身都係喺外圍賽勉強靠得失球入到League B，面對外圍賽League B個range入面排頭兩位嘅圭亞那同牙買加根本冇得打。第二位之爭就落喺圭亞那同安提瓜度，兩隊都會喺最後兩埸打牙買加同阿魯巴，得失球差係關鍵，不過暫時都係圭亞那稍勝一籌，畢竟尋日六分波先大炒完安提瓜。"},{"pid":"d1c50b4afb3d3a220e0007c95d8c7e551c912346","tid":1657562,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:28:06.000Z","msg":"樓主國難緊仲講波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n拉....美拿"},{"pid":"ff40360043b44f1ac4412509a62aff47c8c20412","tid":1657562,"uid":73381,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:51:15.000Z","msg":"依啲島國會唔會有咩宿敵？好似印尼馬拉咁？"},{"pid":"ad75d8aa712a5ecbd21347f7450ef7a7fe49a42f","tid":1657562,"uid":202348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d1c50b4afb3d3a220e0007c95d8c7e551c912346","tid":1657562,"uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T09:28:06.000Z","msg":"樓主國難緊仲講波<img src=\"/a